<h3 id="Step-3:-Blueprint-for-applying-Affinity-on-the-Deployments."><span id="GeographicalDeploymentofExpertflowCXwithRedundancy-Step3:BlueprintforapplyingAffinityontheDeployments."></span>Step 3: Blueprint for applying Affinity on the Deployments.
