<h2 id="Import-your-own-certificates"><span id="GeographicalDeploymentofExpertflowCXwithRedundancy-Importyourowncertificates"></span>Import your own certificates
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
