 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>Once all expertflow service pods are completely&nbsp; up and running, execute these steps for media channel icons to render successfully,</p>
<p>Run the minio-helper pod using</p>
<code-snippet class="theme-code-snippet">
 <scroll-shadow>
  <div data-component="code">
   <pre><code>kubectl apply -f scripts/minio-helper.yaml
</code></pre>
  </div>
